    <section class="section section--information" ng-show="page === 'information'">
        <p>Our wedding ceremony and reception will be held on Saturday, May 23, 2015 at Terrace on the Park, an iconic landmark built to be the heliport used during the 1960’s Worlds Fair in Queens, New York. Terrace on the Park is located at 52-11 111th Street, Flushing Meadows Park. <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/52-11+111th+St,+Corona,+NY+11368/@40.752004,-73.848982,14z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x89c25fd0f5c263e9:0xec468ba86d69aad7">Click here for directions.</a></p>
        <p>The wedding ceremony will begin at 4 PM. Please try to arrive early to allow sufficient time for all guests to be seated.</p>
        <p>We have reserved a number of guest rooms at two Holiday Inn locations in Queens. The most affordable option ($165 a night plus tax) is the <a href="http://www.holidayinn.com/hotels/us/en/corona/nycoa/hoteldetail?qAdlt=1&qBrs=6c.hi.ex.rs.ic.cp.in.sb.cw.cv.ul.vn&qChld=0&qFRA=1&qGRM=0&qGrpCd=FAD&qPSt=0&qRRSrt=rt&qRef=df&qRms=1&qRpn=1&qRpp=12&qSHp=1&qSmP=3&qSrt=sBR&qWch=0&srb_u=1&icdv=99801505&icdv=99801505">Holiday Inn LaGuardia Airport</a>, which is walking distance from the wedding venue, adjacent to Flushing Meadows Park, and close to LaGuardia Airport. <a href="http://www.holidayinn.com/hotels/us/en/corona/nycoa/hoteldetail?qAdlt=1&qBrs=6c.hi.ex.rs.ic.cp.in.sb.cw.cv.ul.vn&qChld=0&qFRA=1&qGRM=0&qGrpCd=FAD&qPSt=0&qRRSrt=rt&qRef=df&qRms=1&qRpn=1&qRpp=12&qSHp=1&qSmP=3&qSrt=sBR&qWch=0&srb_u=1&icdv=99801505&icdv=99801505">Click here to reserve at our group rate</a>, or dial 1 (877) 834-3613 and mention the hotel name and the Faden-Hernandez Wedding.</p>
        <p>For those who wish to stay closer to Manhattan, we have also reserved rooms at the <a href="http://www.ihg.com/holidayinn/hotels/us/en/long-island-city/lgali/hoteldetail?qAdlt=1&qBrs=6c.hi.ex.rs.ic.cp.in.sb.cw.cv.ul.vn&qChld=0&qFRA=1&qGRM=0&qGrpCd=FHW&qPSt=0&qRRSrt=rt&qRef=df&qRms=1&qRpn=1&qRpp=12&qSHp=1&qSmP=3&qSrt=sBR&qWch=0&srb_u=1&icdv=99801505&icdv=99801505">Holiday Inn Long Island City (Manhattan View)</a>, which is a quick subway ride from Times Square, Bryant Park, Rockefeller Center, Williamsburg, and other tourist attractions. <a href="http://www.ihg.com/holidayinn/hotels/us/en/long-island-city/lgali/hoteldetail?qAdlt=1&qBrs=6c.hi.ex.rs.ic.cp.in.sb.cw.cv.ul.vn&qChld=0&qFRA=1&qGRM=0&qGrpCd=FHW&qPSt=0&qRRSrt=rt&qRef=df&qRms=1&qRpn=1&qRpp=12&qSHp=1&qSmP=3&qSrt=sBR&qWch=0&srb_u=1&icdv=99801505&icdv=99801505">Click here to reserve at our group rate</a>, or dial 1 (877) 834-3613 and mention the hotel name and the Faden-Hernandez Wedding.</p>
        <p>Shuttles will be provided from both hotels to the wedding venue.</p>
