    <section class="section section--gifts" ng-show="page === 'gifts'">
        <p>We do not have a formal registry. If you wish to leave us a wedding gift, we would be greatly appreciative of a monetary gift to help us achieve our goals: enhancing and investing in our home and shared business, Majestic Tattoo NYC, traveling, and saving money.</p>
        <p>Please make checks out to Adal Hernandez <strong>OR</strong> Lily Faden. Please contact us directly if you wish to send a check in the mail by emailing us at <a href="mailto:adalandlily@gmail.com">adalandlily@gmail.com</a>.</p>
